Scheer Rowlett | Wealth Management Canada                      Wealth Management CanadaHomeAbout UsFind a Wealth ManagerWealth Management CompaniesTips to Find a Wealth ManagerContact Us       Scheer RowlettAbout	Founded in 1990, Scheer, Rowlett & Associates Investment Management Ltd. (Scheer Rowlett) is an independently owned investment management firm specializing in Canadian equity investments adhering to a value style. Using a fundamental, bottom-up approach, Scheer Rowlett has a strong track record of generating consistent returns and added value in both up and down markets. They currently manage over $5.6 billion in assets for pension funds, mutual funds, corporations, institutional and high net worth investors.  Scheer Rowlett is part of Connor, Clark & Lunn Financial Group, Canada’s second largest independently owned multi-boutique asset management firm responsible for the investment of approximately $46 billion in financial assets through its affiliated investment managers on behalf of institutional, private and retail clients.  Source: Scheer RowlettUnique Value PropositionScheer Rowlett’s investment philosophy is founded on a belief that efficiencies in the equity market are realized over mid- to long-term periods.  We also believe that a company’s earning ability, driven by its capital structure and competitive position, provides transparency to the company’s intrinsic worth. Based on this philosophy, we seek to invest in undervalued companies with strong or improving fundamentals, healthy financial positions and proven management.  Scheer Rowlett strives to deliver superior, risk-adjusted returns over the long term in both up and down markets. Our unwavering commitment to this investment philosophy forms the basis upon which we employ our investment process.  Source: Scheer RowlettAUM ($bil) 					$ 2.8Year Founded 1990Address 181 University Avenue, Suite 300 Toronto, Ontario M5H 3M7Key Personnel Lloyd E. Rowlett, President and Chief Portfolio Manager Ro