Capital Markets

Company Overview of Scheer, Rowlett & Associates Investment Management Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Scheer, Rowlett & Associates Investment Management Ltd. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm manages mutual funds for its clients. It manages separate client focused equity and balanced portfolios through sub-advisory arrangements. The firm invests in the public equity markets of Canada. It invests in value stocks of companies. It employs fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock selection process while making its investments. The firm was founded in 1998 and is based in Ontario, Canada. Scheer, Rowlett & Associates Investment Management Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Connor, Clark & Lunn Investment Management Ltd.


