 About Us 




About Us
 


People
 


Scheer Rowlett in the Community
 


Affiliates
 


Contact Us
 





Scheer, Rowlett & Associates Investment Ltd originally operated as Crown Life Investment Management Inc. (CLIMCO) and was founded in 1990 by the Crown Life Insurance Company. Prior to the formation of CLIMCO, Crown Life managed pooled funds dating back to 1973. In mid-1998, CLIMCO changed its name to Scheer, Rowlett & Associates Investment Management Ltd. at which time the investment professionals and Connor, Clark & Lunn Financial Group (CC&L Financial Group) became owners in the firm. In January of 2001, Crown Life sold its remaining ownership in Scheer Rowlett.  Using a fundamental, bottom-up approach, we have built a strong track record while adhering to a disciplined value approach. We currently manage  in assets for pension plans, mutual funds, corporations, institutional, endowments, foundations and high net worth investors. Scheer Rowlett is part of Connor, Clark & Lunn Financial Group, an independently owned multi-boutique asset management firm whose affiliates are collectively responsible for  in assets under management on behalf of institutional, private and retail clients.







